                           <q xml:lang="gez"><lb n="1"/>ሰላም፡ ለከ፡ ተክለ፡ ሃይማኖት፡ ምሉዕ፡ ሞገስ፡ ወጸጋ፡
                    <lb n="2"/> ስፉሕ፡ አዕጹቅ፡ ወይን፡ እንበለ፡ ንትጋ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis" resp="PRS9602Turaev"/>
                           </q>
                           <note>The excerpt from the hymn encompasses 11 strophes.</note>
